<body>
    <!-- Top Nav Bar -->
<!-- Top Nav Bar -->
<%- include('./partials/navbar.ejs') %>

    <!-- Header -->
    <header>
        <h1>Donation Process Overview</h1>
    </header>

    <!-- Main Content Section -->
    <main id="donation-process-overview">
        
        <!-- Introduction -->
        <section class="content-section">
            <p>Understanding the blood donation process can help ease any concerns you may have and prepare you for a smooth and positive experience. Here is a step-by-step guide to what you can expect during your blood donation journey.</p>
        </section>

        <!-- Steps of the Donation Process -->
        <section class="content-section">
            <div class="step">
                <h3 style="text-align: center;">Step 1: Registration</h3>
                <!-- <img src="path/to/registration-icon.png" alt="Registration Icon" class="step-icon"> -->
                <p>Upon arrival, you will register and provide some personal information, including your identification. This helps us maintain a safe and organized donation environment.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="step">
                <h3 style="text-align: center;">Step 2: Health Screening</h3>
                <!-- <img src="path/to/health-screening-icon.png" alt="Health Screening Icon" class="step-icon"> -->
                <p>A brief health screening will be conducted to ensure you are eligible to donate blood. This includes a questionnaire about your health history and a quick physical checkup.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="step">
                <h3 style="text-align: center;">Step 3: Donation</h3>
                <!-- <img src="path/to/donation-icon.png" alt="Donation Icon" class="step-icon"> -->
                <p>The actual blood donation typically takes about 10-15 minutes. You will be seated comfortably, and a trained staff member will collect your blood using sterile equipment.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="step">
                <h3 style="text-align: center;">Step 4: Rest and Refreshments</h3>
                <!-- <img src="path/to/rest-refreshments-icon.png" alt="Rest and Refreshments Icon" class="step-icon"> -->
                <p>After donating, you will be guided to a rest area where you can relax and enjoy some refreshments. This helps replenish your energy and ensures you feel well before leaving.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="step">
                <h3 style="text-align: center;">Step 5: After Donation</h3>
                <!-- <img src="path/to/after-donation-icon.png" alt="After Donation Icon" class="step-icon"> -->
                <p>We recommend drinking plenty of fluids and avoiding strenuous activities for the rest of the day. Your body will quickly replenish the donated blood, and you can return to your routine.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Call to Action -->
        <section class="content-section">
            <h3>Ready to Donate?</h3>
            <p>We are here to answer any questions and help you through every step of the donation process. Schedule an appointment or contact us for more information.</p>
            <a href="/appiontment" class="cta-button">Schedule an Appointment</a>
        </section>

    </main>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <%- include('./partials/footer.ejs') %>
</body>
</html>